    <div class="Container">
        <h1>Investigation</h1>
	<h2>Research on Existing Systems:</h2>
	<p>To aid me with creating this brief I researched and analysed different websites that have interactive informative systems. I looked at different database websites to find my chosen dataset and to simultaneously research on how interactive websites appear. I started working on my website using existing HTML code that I had written earlier this year. This website simply used heading tags, hyperlinks and image tags. I used this basic code to start my website and then I added more detail and CSS. While I was searching for a dataset, I was also examining and analysing the database websites to get a feel for how they were structured and how they functioned. Kaggle. For example, I saw the repeated use of a navigation bar which I thought would definitely enhance user experience and make the website more accessible overall. I decided to implement this into my own website along with a contents page. </p>
	<h2>Research on my dataset/topic</h2>
	<p>Healthy Corals are the foundation of our oceanâ€™s food chain. Healthy coral reefs contribute to fishing and tourism, providing millions of jobs and contributing to economies all over the world. Scientists develop important drugs from coral reef organisms as treatments for cancer and viruses. But corals are threatened by pollution and climate change. Our human activity causes pollution to increase and climate change to occur quicker. So it is important to protect the coral reefs.</p>
